    "description": "Game Master Module is a tool for expanding the experience of your online RPG sessions.<br />\r\nThanks to the ability to set up a personalized board with miniatures, you can play a unique game alone or with friends.<br />\r\nTransfer all your designs and dreams to easy-to-use virtual worlds.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay a 100-unit battle or a game of chess. You are only limited by your imagination!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBring your favorite RPG system to the Game Master Module.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur game is distinguished by:<br />\r\n-ability to load any 3D models (FBX, OBJ, STL), so you can play the game in any world<br />\r\n-possibility of creating any board size<br />\r\n-possibility of loading any graphics as the board background (JPG, PNG, BMP)<br />\r\n-Easy-to-use terrain construction<br />\r\n-dedicated notebook for each unit and for the game master<br />\r\n-three dedicated modes of moving units: square grid, hexagonal grid and no grid<br />\r\n-ability to edit colors and names of units<br />\r\n-dice rolling simulator<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPost-release features:<br />\r\n-2D board mode<br />\r\n-Multiplayer<br />\r\n-Fog of war<br />\r\n-Creator of corridors and rooms<br />\r\n-Creator of objects on the board (hills, rivers, lakes, forests, etc.)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease contact us: info@mielczarekart.com",
